=== Diagonalizing a quadratic Hamiltonian using matrix description ===
Bogoliubov transformation lets us diagonalize a quadratic Hamiltonian
:formula_44
by just diagonalizing the matrix formula_45. 
In the notations above, it is important to distinguish the operator formula_46 and the numeric matrix formula_47.
This fact can be seen by rewriting formula_46 as
